otcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4ba6b61753d4688c2f3d31617a0461e20283e9d","tid":1610981,"uid":146621,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T01:24:21.000Z","msg":"喊左，點解一個外國記者都明嘅野<br />\n自己老豆老母會唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11d5bdfd0d1e637581c0163918052ce28462fe2c","tid":1610981,"uid":8562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T01:32:46.000Z","msg":"一定會等到民主來到"},{"pid":"4f378867de5a9f507c4a47d07b95dc11f3f5dd14","tid":1610981,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T01:46:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8005c3648fc8d5a6e49e960f373146942257e42a","tid":1610981,"uid":17103,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b4ba6b61753d4688c2f3d31617a0461e20283e9d","tid":1610981,"uid":146621,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T01:24:21.000Z","msg":"喊左，點解一個外國記者都明嘅野<br />\n自己老豆老母會唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T01:52:24.000Z","msg":"你要套落佢地年齡同經歷.  記住唔好期望你可以教化到人.<br />\n好多時人係要自省中先會明白道理 (有講: 唔見棺材唔流淚)"},{"pid":"6ca5fc698ea8e857b7bc511fe4a46e782dc8d910","tid":1610981,"uid":146621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8005c3648fc8d5a6e49e960f373146942257e42a","tid":1610981,"uid":17103,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b4ba6b61753d4688c2f3d31617a0461e20283e9d","tid":1610981,"uid":146621,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T01:24:21.000Z","msg":"喊左，點解一個外國記者都明嘅野<br />\n自己老豆老母會唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T01:52:24.000Z","msg":"你要套落佢地年齡同經歷.  記住唔好期望你可以教化到人.<br />\n好多時人係要自省中先會明白道理 (有講: 唔見棺材唔流淚)"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T01:53:27.00